reviewText: This is the same park souvenir DVD that's been sold for years. This is nothing to do with the 50th anniversary other than a 2 minute long bonus feature. Picture isn't even close to real item...

When I bought this dvd I thought it was all 50 years Disneyland..
But by the first moments I saw this dvd was EXACT the same as the REMEMBER THE MOMENTS dvd!!
So If you have that do not buy it then.
for people who doesn't have that dvd it is a good dvd for preporation for going to Anaheim.
